Boone has always been known for its beauty and charm and is home to Appalachian State University.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>RubiTrux's goal is to offer high quality Jeep conversions on new and used Jeeps. We specialize in half-cab conversions on Jeep Wrangler Unlimiteds (manufactured from 2004-2006) and moderate to extreme modifications to JK Wranglers (2007-current).</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>RubiTrux Conversions is the Jeep division of High Country 4x4 Center, and all of the work is done by our professional staff. High Country 4x4 Center has served the Boone area for the past 15 years doing modifications to all types of 4x4 vehicles.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Our 04-06 Unlimited conversions turn these Jeeps into a light-duty, fun truck. Jeep offered the Scrambler from 1981 until 1986 and has since not offered a truck with a removable top. Here at RubiTrux, we have the answer for Jeep Lovers everywhere with our conversion package.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>These awesome little trucks become a reality by using an AEV Brute half cab, which has been adapted to fit the 2004-2006 Unlimited. The conversions also include our custom RubiTrux bulkhead, Line-x spray-in bedliner, and labor. Current pricing on this half cab conversion is $5,250.00, which includes painting the top to match the color of the Jeep.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>From there, these halfcab trucks can be left as is or customized with a myriad of aftermarket equipment from Warn, Rubicon Express, ARB, Rugged Ridge, Old Man Emu, AEV, and many others.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>As our slogan says, there are unlimited possibilities!</p>\n<div style=\"font-size: 18px; margin-top: 15px;\"><a title=\"Let Us Build the Jeep of Your Dreams, Fill Out This Form...\" onclick=\"window.open(this.href, null, 'height=1248, width=680, toolbar=0, location=0, status=1, scrollbars=1, resizable=1,top=20,left=200 '); return false\" href=\"http://rubitrux.wufoo.com/forms/z7x3p3/\"><img style=\"float: right;\" src=\"https://cdn.rubitrux.com/media/rubitrux/custom-build-request-large.png\" alt=\"Custom Jeep Build Request Form\"></a>\n<h2>Interested in a Custom RubiTrux Build of Your Very Own?</h2>\n<h3>From Mild to Wild, we can build you the Jeep of your dreams.
